5 Connect & share

<p>Once you’ve <a href="/processmap/signup">created a free account</a>, there are lots of ways you can connect with the climbing world.</p>

<ul class="sd-checklist">
  <li>Follow your friends and other climbers- just click the ‘Follow’ button on their account page.</li>
  <li><a href="/article/cragchat">Discuss areas, routes, trips and ascents</a> with your friends and the climbing community.</li>
  <li><a href="/article/favoritecrags">Monitor the action at your favorite crags</a></li>
  <li><a href="/article/trips">Plan trips and find partners</a></li>
  <li><a href="/article/feeds">Use RSS feeds to stay connected</a></li>
  <li><a href="/article/facebookpublishing">Publish your ascents on Facebook</a></li>
</ul>
